00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:11,196
First we demonstrate that tree is absent. APT update refreshes repository metadata, and APT install adds the package through the supported package manager instead of copying an unmanaged binary.

2
00:00:11,196 --> 00:00:20,462
D P K G query verifies package state. We then create the exact one-line package report required by the lab, including a final newline.

3
00:00:20,462 --> 00:00:30,886
The pipeline extracts field four from every access-log row, sorts equal status codes together, counts adjacent values, and swaps the count and status into the requested order.

4
00:00:30,886 --> 00:00:40,923
The final cat command exposes both deliverables. In particular, the status report must contain four zero four followed by three before the automated check can pass.
